flowchart TB
  User[Usuário local] --> Frontend[React + Vite UI]
  Frontend --> Backend[FastAPI Backend]
  Backend --> Config[Pydantic Settings]
  Backend --> Documents[Document Service]
  Backend --> RAG[RAG Services]
  Backend --> Chat[Chat Service]
  Documents --> Parser[Text/PDF Parser]
  Documents --> Chunker[Chunking Service]
  RAG --> Embeddings[Embedding Adapter]
  RAG --> VectorStore[Local Vector Store]
  Chat --> Prompt[Prompt Builder]
  Chat --> OllamaChat[Ollama Chat Adapter]
  Embeddings --> OllamaEmbed[Ollama Embedding Adapter]
  OllamaChat --> Ollama[Ollama Local Runtime]
  OllamaEmbed --> Ollama
  Ollama --> Gemma4[Gemma 4]
  Ollama --> EmbeddingGemma[EmbeddingGemma]
  VectorStore --> SQLite[(SQLite Local DB)]
  Documents --> SQLite
  Chat --> SQLite
